(257, 1, '2019-12-26 08:06:47', '2019-12-26 08:06:47', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Selection Sharer is a mobile-friendly social share plugin that shows a floating popover that allows highlighted/selected text to be shared on Facebook, LinkedIn or via email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On mobile devices, instead of better user experiences, the plugin will screen a social sharing popunder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It also has the ability, when a Facebook App ID is given, to display the Facebook sharing link inside the share popover.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This Plugin has been used on Nepal Magazine, Medium, and The Kathmandu Post</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How to use ?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To use this plugin, you need to make sure \"selection-sharer.css\", \"jQuery\" &amp; \"selection-sharer.js\" files are included correctly.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">&lt;script src=\"//code.jquery.com/jquery.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"selection-sharer.css\"&gt;\n&lt;script src=\"selection-sharer.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 2. Specify the Facebook App ID in the meta tags (OPTIONAL). </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">&lt;meta property=\"fb:app_id\" content=\"CONTENT HERE\"&gt;\n&lt;meta property=\"fb:admins\" content=\"CONTENT HERE\"&gt;</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Then initialize the plugin on the target text content and done.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">$(\'p\').selectionSharer();</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4.  Or ... </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">var sharer = new SelectionSharer(\'p\');</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. Override the default CSS rules to create your own styles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">#selectionSharerPopover:after {\n  content: \'\';\n  display: block;\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: -3px;\n  left: 50%;\n  margin-left: -4px;\n  width: 8px;\n  height: 8px;\n  -webkit-transform: rotate(45deg);\n  transform: rotate(45deg);\n  background: #262625;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 2px #262625;\n}\n\n#selectionSharerPopunder {\n  position: absolute;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 0px;\n  transition: height 0.5s ease-in-out;\n  background: #ccc;\n  border: none;\n  box-shadow: inset 0px 10px 5px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0px -10px 5px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n  border-radius: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jqueryscript.net/demo/Share-Selected-Text-On-Twitter-Email-jQuery-Selection-Sharer/\">DEMO</a>           <a href=\"https://www.jqueryscript.net/download/Share-Selected-Text-On-Twitter-Email-jQuery-Selection-Sharer.zip\">DOWNLOAD</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Selected TEXT share in Social ( Facebook, Twitter, Email)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'selected-text-share-in-social-facebook-twitter-email', '', '', '2023-05-04 05:13:42', '2023-05-04 05:13:42', '', 0, 'https://www.ayushshrestha.com.np/?p=257', 0, 'post', '', 0),
